require(data.table)

require(anytime)

require(ggplot2)

matches=readRDS(“~/Desktop/IE 582/IE582Fall2018_project_files/df9b1196-e3cf-4cc7-9159-f236fe738215_matches.rds”)

odds=readRDS(“~/Desktop/IE 582/IE582Fall2018_project_files/df9b1196-e3cf-4cc7-9159-f236fe738215_odd_details.rds”)

matches=unique(matches)

matches[ ,match_date := anydate(date)]

matches[ ,match_time := anytime(date)]

matches[,c(“HomeGoals”,“AwayGoals”):=tstrsplit(score,‘:’)]

matches=matches[complete.cases(matches)]

matches[,HomeGoals:=as.numeric(HomeGoals)]

matches[,AwayGoals:=as.numeric(AwayGoals)]

matches[,TotalGoals:=HomeGoals+AwayGoals]

matches[,OverUnder:=0]

matches[TotalGoals>2.5,OverUnder:=1]

odds=unique(odds)

odds[ ,match_date := anydate(date)]

odds_ov_un=odds[betType==‘ou’ & totalhandicap==‘2.5’]

odds_ov_un[,totalhandicap:=NULL]

odds_ov_un=odds_ov_un[order(matchId, oddtype,bookmaker,date)]

odds_ov_un_final=odds_ov_un[,list(final_odd=odd[.N]),by=list(matchId,oddtype,bookmaker)]

wide_odds_final=dcast(odds_ov_un_final,matchId~oddtype+bookmaker,value.var=‘final_odd’)

pinnacle_over_under_final=odds_ov_un_final[bookmaker==‘Pinnacle’]

pinnacle_wide_final=dcast(pinnacle_over_under_final,matchId~oddtype,value.var=‘final_odd’)

odds_oddtype=odds[order(matchId, oddtype,bookmaker,date)]

odds_oddtype_final=odds[,list(final_odd=odd[.N]),by=list(matchId,oddtype,bookmaker)]

pinnacle_oddtype=odds_oddtype_final[bookmaker==‘Pinnacle’]

pinnacle_wide_oddtype=dcast(pinnacle_oddtype,matchId~oddtype,value.var=‘final_odd’)

pinnacle_wide_oddtype[,over:=NULL]

pinnacle_wide_oddtype[,under:=NULL]

merged_odds_pinnacle=merge(pinnacle_wide_final,pinnacle_wide_oddtype,by=‘matchId’)

merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle<-merge(merged_odds_pinnacle,matches,by=‘matchId’)

merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle<-merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle[,-9:-19]

merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle_withoutmatchid<-merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle[,-1]

merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle_withoutmatchid_forpca<-merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle_wit houtmatchid[,-8]

merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle_withoutmatchid_forpca_scaled=scale(merged_odds_final_newcategory_

pinnacle_withoutmatchid_forpca, center = TRUE, scale = TRUE)

PCA_pinnacle<-prcomp(merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle_withoutmatchid_forpca_scaled)

summary(PCA_pinnacle)

str(PCA_pinnacle)

PCA_pinnacle$x

merged_odds_pinnacle_combined<-cbind(merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle_withoutmatchid,PCA_pinnacle$x[,1:2])

ggplot(merged_odds_pinnacle_combined,aes(PC1,PC2,col=OverUnder,fill=OverUnder))+geom_point(shape=21,col=“blue”) + gtitle(“Pinnacle PCA”)

cor(merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle_withoutmatchid,merged_odds_pinnacle_combined[,9:10])

3.1. Task 1 b :

dist_pinnacle<-dist(scale(t(merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle_withoutmatchid[,-8]), center=TRUE, scale=TRUE),method = “euclidean”)

mds_pinnacle<-cmdscale(dist_pinnacle,eig = TRUE,x.ret = TRUE)

mds.var<-round(mds_pinnacle\(eig/sum(mds_pinnacle\)eig)*100,1)

mds.values.pinnacle<-mds_pinnacle$points

mds.data.pinnacle<-data.frame(sample=rownames(mds.values.pinnacle), X=mds.values.pinnacle[,1], Y=mds.values.pinnacle[,2])

ggplot(data=mds.data.pinnacle, aes(x=X, y=Y, label=sample)) + geom_text() + theme_bw() + xlab(paste(“MDS1 -”, mds.var[1], “%”, sep="“)) + ylab(paste(”MDS2 - “, mds.var[2],”%“, sep=”“)) + ggtitle(”Pinnacle MDS with method Euclidean distance")

dist_pinnacle_manhattan<-dist(scale(t(merged_odds_final_newcategory_pinnacle_withoutmatchid[,-8]), center=TRUE, scale=TRUE),method = “manhattan”)

mds_pinnacle_manhattan<-cmdscale(dist_pinnacle_manhattan,eig = TRUE,x.ret = TRUE)

mds.var<-round(mds_pinnacle_manhattan\(eig/sum(mds_pinnacle_manhattan\)eig)*100,1)

mds.values.pinnacle_manhattan<-mds_pinnacle_manhattan$points

mds.data.pinnacle_manhattan<-data.frame(sample=rownames(mds.values.pinnacle_manhattan), X=mds.values.pinnacle_manhattan[,1], Y=mds.values.pinnacle_manhattan[,2])

ggplot(data=mds.data.pinnacle_manhattan, aes(x=X, y=Y, label=sample)) + geom_text() + theme_bw() + xlab(paste(“MDS1 -”, mds.var[1], “%”, sep="“)) + ylab(paste(”MDS2 - “, mds.var[2],”%“, sep=”“)) + ggtitle(”Pinnacle MDS with method Manhattan distance")

set.seed(12)

noise_channelR=matrix(runif(40000,0,0.1),200,200,1)

noise_channelG=matrix(runif(40000,0,0.1),200,200,2)

noise_channelB=matrix(runif(40000,0,0.1),200,200,3)

husky=as.matrix(husky)

noisy_husky=noise_channelR + noise_channelG + noise_channelB + image(husky)

plot(1, type=“n”, xlim=c(0, 200), ylim=c(0, 200))

rasterImage(noisy_husky,0, 0, 200, 200, interpolate = FALSE)
